    "LilycoveCity_ContestLobby_Text_WhichTopic1": "Which topic would you like?",
    "LilycoveCity_ContestLobby_Text_ExplainContests": "A POKMON CONTEST involves four\\nTRAINERS entering one POKMON each\\lin competitive judging.\\pA CONTEST has two stages of judging,\\nprimary and secondary.\\pPrimary judging is a popularity poll\\ninvolving the audience.\\pSecondary judging features appeals\\nby the POKMON using their moves.\\pPlan appeals carefully to earn the\\nmost attention of the JUDGE and\\lexcite the audience.\\lDo your best to stand out.\\pThe primary and secondary scores are\\nadded at the end.\\pThe POKMON garnering the highest\\nscore is declared the winner.",
    "LilycoveCity_ContestLobby_Text_ExplainContestTypes": "There are five kinds of CONTESTS.\\pCOOL, BEAUTY, CUTE, SMART, and\\nTOUGH are the five categories.\\pChoose the CONTEST that is right for\\nthe POKMON you plan to enter.",
    "LilycoveCity_ContestLobby_Text_ExplainContestRanks": "There are four ranks of POKMON\\nCONTESTS.\\pNORMAL, SUPER, HYPER, and MASTER\\nare the four ranks.\\pIn the NORMAL Rank, any POKMON may\\nenter.\\pAny POKMON that won a NORMAL Rank\\nCONTEST may move up to the SUPER Rank\\lin the same category.\\pIn the same way, a SUPER Rank winner\\ncan move up to the HYPER Rank, and\\la HYPER Rank winner can advance to\\lthe MASTER Rank in the same category.\\pA POKMON that won in the MASTER Rank\\nmay compete in the MASTER Rank as\\loften as its TRAINER wants.",
    "LilycoveCity_ContestLobby_Text_EnterWhichRank": "Which Rank would you like to enter?",
    "LilycoveCity_ContestLobby_Text_EnterWhichContest1": "Which CONTEST would you like to enter?",
    "LilycoveCity_ContestLobby_Text_EnterWhichPokemon1": "Which POKMON would you like to enter?",
    "LilycoveCity_ContestLobby_Text_MonNotQualifiedForRank": "I'm terribly sorry, but your POKMON\\nis not qualified to compete at this\\lRank yet",
    "LilycoveCity_ContestLobby_Text_EggCannotTakePart": "I'm sorry, but an EGG cannot take part\\nin a POKMON CONTEST.",
    "LilycoveCity_ContestLobby_Text_MonInNoConditionForContest": "Your POKMON appears to be in no\\ncondition to take part in a CONTEST",
    "LilycoveCity_ContestLobby_Text_AlreadyWonEnterAnyway": "Oh, but that RIBBON\\pYour POKMON has won this CONTEST\\nbefore, hasn't it?\\pWould you like to enter it in this\\nCONTEST anyway?",
    "LilycoveCity_ContestLobby_Text_ConfirmContestMon": "Is that your CONTEST POKMON?",
    "LilycoveCity_ContestLobby_Text_YourMonIsEntryNum4": "Okay, your POKMON will be entered\\nin this CONTEST.\\pYour POKMON is Entry No. 4.\\nThe CONTEST will begin shortly.",
    "LilycoveCity_ContestLobby_Text_ComeThroughHere": "Please come in through here.\\nGood luck!",
    "LilycoveCity_ContestLobby_Text_PokemonWonWeHavePrize": "Congratulations! Your POKMON is the\\nCONTEST winner!\\pWe have your prize right here.\\nPlease, right this way!",
    "LilycoveCity_ContestLobby_Text_ComeBackForPrizeLater": "Please come back for your prize\\nlater on.",
    "ContestHall_Text_GettingStartedParticipantsAsFollows": "MC: Hello! We're just getting started\\nwith a {STR_VAR_3} Rank POKMON\\l{STR_VAR_2}!\\pThe participating TRAINERS and their\\nPOKMON are as follows:",
    "ContestHall_Text_GettingStartedParticipantsAsFollowsLink": "MC: Hello! We're just getting started\\nwith a 4-player linked POKMON\\l{STR_VAR_2}!\\pThe participating TRAINERS and their\\nPOKMON are as follows:",
    "ContestHall_Text_EntryXTrainersMon": "MC: Entry No. {STR_VAR_2}!\\n{STR_VAR_1}'s {STR_VAR_3}!",
    "ContestHall_Text_SeenContestantsAudienceWillVote": "MC: We've just seen the four POKMON\\ncontestants.\\pNow it's time for primary judging!\\pThe audience will vote on their\\nfavorite POKMON contestants.\\pWithout any further ado, let the\\nvoting begin!",
    "ContestHall_Text_VotingUnderWay": "Voting under way",
    "ContestHall_Text_VotingCompleteLetsAppeal": "Voting is now complete!\\pWhile the votes are being tallied,\\nlet's move on to secondary judging!\\pThe second stage of judging is the\\nmuch anticipated appeal time!\\pMay the contestants amaze us with\\nsuperb appeals of dazzling moves!\\pLet's see a little enthusiasm!\\nLet's appeal!",
    "ContestHall_Text_ThatsItForJudging": "MC: That's it for judging!",
    "ContestHall_Text_ThankYouForAppeals": "Thank you all for a most wonderful\\ndisplay of quality appeals!\\pThis concludes all judging!\\nThank you for your fine efforts!",
    "ContestHall_Text_JudgeLooksReady": "Now, all that remains is the pulse-\\npounding proclamation of the winner.\\pThe JUDGE looks ready to make\\nthe announcement!",
    "ContestHall_Text_WeWillNowDeclareWinner": "JUDGE: We will now declare the winner!",
