    "ContestHall_Text_OnlyRegister4Players": "I only register four players for\\nPOKMON CONTESTS.\\pIf three other players link up, all\\nfour may enter the same CONTEST.\\pWould you like to take part?",
    "LilycoveCity_ContestLobby_Text_ProgressWillBeSaved": "Before entering a CONTEST, your\\nprogress will be saved.",
    "LilycoveCity_ContestLobby_Text_ParticipateAnotherTime": "We hope you will participate another\\ntime.",
    "LilycoveCity_ContestLobby_Text_EnterContest2": "Would you like to enter a CONTEST?",
    "LilycoveCity_ContestLobby_Text_Explain4PlayerContest": "When four players are ready, connect\\nover a Game Link cable, and register\\lwith me, please.\\pPlease choose the same CONTEST\\nas your fellow contestants.\\pThe CONTEST begins as soon as all\\nplayers register their entry.\\pAfter that, the usual CONTEST rules\\napply.",
