    "Route117_Text_SeeWifeIfYoudLikeMeToRaiseMon": "I'm the DAY-CARE MAN.\\pI help take care of the precious\\nPOKMON of TRAINERS.\\pIf you'd like me to raise your POKMON,\\nhave a word with my wife.",
    "Route117_Text_DoYouWantEgg": "Ah, it's you!\\pWe were raising your POKMON,\\nand my goodness, were we surprised!\\pYour POKMON had an EGG!\\pWe don't know how it got there,\\nbut your POKMON had it.\\pYou do want it, yes?",
    "Route117_Text_YourMonIsDoingFine": "Ah, it's you! Good to see you.\\nYour {STR_VAR_1}'s doing fine.",
    "Route117_Text_IllKeepIt": "Well then, I'll keep it.\\nThanks!",
    "Route117_Text_YouHaveNoRoomForIt": "You have no room for it\\nCome back when you've made room.",
