    "gText_Birch_YourePlayer": "Ah, okay!\\pYou're {PLAYER}{KUN} who's moving to my\\nhometown of LITTLEROOT.\\lI get it now!\\p",
    "gText_Birch_AreYouReady": "All right, are you ready?\\pYour very own adventure is about\\nto unfold.\\pTake courage, and leap into the\\nworld of POKMON where dreams,\\ladventure, and friendships await!\\pWell, I'll be expecting you later.\\nCome see me in my POKMON LAB.\\p",
