    "BerryBlender_Text_SeeMyMasteryInAction": "BLEND MASTER: Hmmm! So, you wish to\\nsee my mastery in action?",
    "BerryBlender_Text_TooBusyNowIsee": "Hmmm!\\pSo, you are too busy now, I see!\\pBut fear not!\\nI shall be here all day!\\lHurry back from your errand!",
    "BerryBlender_Text_BlendMasterNoBerries": "Hmmm!\\pYou haven't got a single BERRY!\\pI shall be here all day!\\nHurry back with some BERRIES!",
    "BerryBlender_Text_BlendMasterKnowHowToMakePokeblocks": "Of course!\\nOf course!\\pIncidentally\\nYou do know how to blend {POKEBLOCK}S\\lfrom BERRIES?",
    "BerryBlender_Text_BlendMasterExplainBerryBlending": "Hmmm!\\pAh, but it is a simple process!\\pWhen the BLENDER's arrow comes to\\nyour marker, just press the A Button.\\pThat's all you have to do.\\pWhen you see how precisely I press\\nthe A Button, you will understand.",
    "BerryBlender_Text_BlendMasterLetsBerryBlender": "Fine!\\pLet's get started, then!\\pAll together with the BLEND MASTER,\\nlet's BERRY BLENDER!",
    "BerryBlender_Text_BlendMasterNoPokeblockCase": "Hmmm!\\pYou don't appear to have gotten\\nthe {POKEBLOCK} CASE!\\pI shall be here all day!\\nObtain the {POKEBLOCK} CASE and hurry back!",
    "BerryBlender_Text_BlendMasterPokeblockCaseFull": "Hmmm!\\pYour {POKEBLOCK} CASE appears to be full!\\pI shall be here all day!\\nUse some {POKEBLOCK}S and hurry back!",
    "BerryBlender_Text_WhoaAwesome": "Whoa!\\nAwesome!",
