    "BerryBlender_Text_QualitiesOfBlendMaster": "Eyes that track the arrow with\\nmachinelike intensity\\pA hand that taps the A Button\\nwith clockwork-like precision\\pPossessing these qualities makes\\nthe BLEND MASTER truly great.",
