    "MossdeepCity_GameCorner_1F_Text_ExplainRequiredMon": "It doesn't look like you have any\\nPOKMON that you can enter\\pWould you like me to explain what\\nkinds of POKMON can enter?",
    "MossdeepCity_GameCorner_1F_Text_ShortJumpingPokemonAllowed": "POKMON JUMP is open to POKMON\\naround 28 inches or less.\\pWhat you can't enter are those\\nPOKMON that can't jump.\\pYou know, like POKMON that only\\nswim, burrow, or fly.\\pThat's all you need to know.",
