    "CableClub_Text_WelcomeWhichDirectCornerRoom": "Welcome to the POKMON WIRELESS\\nCLUB DIRECT CORNER.\\pYou may interact directly with\\nyour friends here.\\pWhich room would you like to\\nenter?",
