    "CableClub_Text_UseBerryCrush": "Would you like to use the\\nBERRY CRUSH System?",
    "CableClub_Text_ExplainBattleModes": "There are three Battle Modes.\\pSINGLE BATTLE is for two TRAINERS\\nwith one or more POKMON each.\\pEach TRAINER can have one POKMON\\nin battle at a time.\\pDOUBLE BATTLE is for two TRAINERS\\nwith two or more POKMON each.\\pEach TRAINER will send out two\\nPOKMON in battle at a time.\\pMULTI BATTLE is for four TRAINERS\\nwith one or more POKMON each.\\pEach TRAINER can have one POKMON\\nin battle at a time.",
    "CableClub_Text_ChooseGroupLeaderOfTwo": "Please decide which of you two\\nwill become the LEADER.\\pThe other player must then choose\\nJOIN GROUP.",
