    "CableClub_Text_ChooseGroupLeader": "Please decide which of you will\\nbecome the GROUP LEADER.\\pThe other players must then choose\\nJOIN GROUP.",
    "CableClub_Text_WelcomeUnionRoomEnter": "Welcome to the POKMON WIRELESS\\nCLUB UNION ROOM.\\pYou may interact directly with\\nother TRAINERS here, some of\\lwhom you may not even know.\\pWould you like to enter the ROOM?",
    "CableClub_Text_UnionRoomInfo": "The TRAINERS in the UNION ROOM\\nwill be those players around you\\lwho have also entered the ROOM.\\pYou may do all sorts of things\\nhere, such as exchanging greetings.\\pYou may enter two POKMON up to\\nLv. 30 for a one-on-one battle.\\pYou may take part in a chat with\\ntwo to five people.\\pOr, you may register a POKMON for\\ntrade.\\pWould you like to enter the ROOM?",
    "CableClub_Text_EnjoyUnionRoom": "I hope you enjoy your time in\\nthe UNION ROOM.",
    "CableClub_Text_FirstTimeRightThisWay": "Hello!\\nMy name is TEALA.\\pThis must be your first time\\nup here.\\pI'll show you how the Wireless\\nCommunication System works.\\pFirst, I need to show you this\\nfloor of our POKMON CENTER.\\pRight this way, please.",
    "CableClub_Text_ExplainWirelessClubFirstTime": "On the top floor, there are two\\nrooms.\\pFirst, the room on the left.\\nIt's the UNION ROOM.\\pYou may link up with TRAINERS\\naround you who have also entered\\lthe UNION ROOM.\\pWith them, you may do things like\\nchat, battle, and trade.\\pSecond, the room on the right is\\nthe DIRECT CORNER.\\pYou may trade or battle POKMON\\nwith your friends in this room.\\pIf the Wireless Adapter isn't\\nconnected, you may still link up\\lusing a GBA Game Link cable.\\pIf that is the case, you must go\\nto the DIRECT CORNER.\\pI hope you enjoy the Wireless \\nCommunication System.",
    "CableClub_Text_AskAboutLinking": "Hello, {PLAYER}!\\pIt's me, TEALA, the POKMON\\nCENTER 2F attendant.\\pIs there something you needed to\\nask me about linking?",
    "CableClub_Text_ExplainWirelessClub": "Let me explain how the POKMON\\nWIRELESS CLUB works.\\pOn this, the top floor, there are\\ntwo rooms.\\pFirst, the room on the left.\\nIt's the UNION ROOM.\\pYou may link up with TRAINERS\\naround you who have also entered\\lthe UNION ROOM.\\pWith them, you may do things like\\nchat, battle, and trade.\\pSecond, the room on the right is\\nthe DIRECT CORNER.\\pYou may trade or battle POKMON\\nwith your friends in this room.\\pSometimes, you may not be able to\\nfind your friends in the UNION ROOM\\lor the DIRECT CORNER.\\pIn that case, please move closer\\nto your friends.\\pIf the Wireless Adapter isn't\\nconnected, you may still link up\\lusing a GBA Game Link cable.\\pIf that is the case, you must go\\nto the DIRECT CORNER.\\pI hope you enjoy the Wireless \\nCommunication System.",
    "CableClub_Text_HopeYouEnjoyWirelessSystem": "I hope you enjoy the Wireless\\nCommunication System.",
