    "EventTicket_Text_ShowOldSeaMap": "The ferry to SLATEPORT is\\pI beg your pardon?\\nCan we sail to this place on the map?\\pI know someone who will help you better.\\nPlease wait.",
    "EventTicket_Text_ThatPass": "The ferry to SLATEPORT is\\pOh?\\nThat PASS",
    "EventTicket_Text_ShowEonTicket": "Aye, mate, are you the one who brought\\nthat mighty odd PASS?\\pI'll tell you, you're trying to reach a\\ntiny spit of an island far in the south.\\pThere's no telling what we'll encounter\\nonce we reach there, aye.\\lThat shivers my timbers!\\pAll aboard!",
    "EventTicket_Text_SouthernIslandSailBack": "Aye, mate, there's nothing here to\\nsee or do on this forgettable island.\\pWhat say we sail back to LILYCOVE?",
    "EventTicket_Text_SailHome": "Aye, right, then!\\nSail home we will!",
    "EventTicket_Text_AsYouLike": "Aye, right, as you like, then.",
    "SouthernIsland_Interior_Text_Sign": "All dreams are but another reality.\\nNever forget",
    "SouthernIsland_Exterior_Text_Sign": "Those whose memories fade seek to\\ncarve them in their hearts",
    "EventTicket_Text_OldSeaMapTooFar": "What's up, youngster?\\pWhat, it's you who's supposed to have\\na tattered old map?\\pLet's have a look.\\n     \\pBoy, this is quite a ways away.\\nI'm afraid I can't help you",
    "EventTicket_Text_BrineyHoldOnASecond": "BRINEY: Hold on a second!\\pWhat's the idea of turning down\\nsomeone that I owe so much to?",
    "EventTicket_Text_BrineyLetsSail": "{PLAYER}{KUN}, I'm terribly sorry.\\pYou came to me seeking my help,\\nand we almost turned you away.\\pWell, let me make things right.\\pWe'll sail right away, of course!\\pLet's find this island on\\nthis OLD SEA MAP!",
    "EventTicket_Text_OddTicketGetOnBoard": "Is it you who brought that odd\\nticket?\\pWhere you're trying to go is an island\\nthat's far, far away.\\pNo one knows what awaits there\\pThe very thought excites my blood\\nas a sailing man!\\pGet on board, youngster!",
    "FarawayIsland_Entrance_Text_SailorReturn": "CAPT. BRINEY can be so maddeningly\\nfickle\\pDo you want to return to LILYCOVE?",
    "BirthIsland_Harbor_Text_SailorReturn": "What an oddly shaped island, eh?\\nDo you want to return to LILYCOVE?",
    "EventTicket_Text_OddTicketsWhereTo": "Is it you who brought those\\nodd tickets?\\p  Hm.\\pThese tickets will get you to islands\\nthat are far, far away.\\pNo one knows what awaits there,\\nor what may happen there.\\pThe very thought excites my blood\\nas a sailing man!\\pGet on board, youngster!\\nWhere shall we sail first?",
    "NavelRock_Harbor_Text_SailorReturn": "Did Did you hear that?\\nThat low growling from deep in there.\\pAre you sure it's safe?\\nDo you think we should leave?",
    "FarawayIsland_Entrance_Text_Sign": "The writing is fading as if it was\\nwritten a long time ago\\pber, 6th day\\nIf any humansets foot here\\lagainet it be a kindhearted pers\\lith that hope, I depar",
    "FarawayIsland_Interior_Text_Mew": "Myuu",
    "gText_AnabelWonSilver": "It's very disappointing",
    "gText_AnabelDefeatSilver": "Okay, I understand",
    "gText_AnabelWonGold": "I'm terribly sorry",
    "gText_AnabelDefeatGold": "Thank you",
    "gText_TuckerWonSilver": "Ahahaha! Aren't you embarrassed?\\nEveryone's watching!",
    "gText_TuckerDefeatSilver": "Grr\\nWhat the",
    "gText_TuckerWonGold": "My DOME ACE title isn't just for show!",
    "gText_TuckerDefeatGold": "Ahahaha!\\nYou're inspiring!",
    "gText_NolandWonSilver": "Way to work!\\nThat was a good lesson, eh?",
    "gText_NolandDefeatSilver": "Good job!\\nYou know what you're doing!",
    "gText_NolandWonGold": "Hey, hey, hey!\\nYou're finished already?",
    "gText_NolandDefeatGold": "What happened here?",
    "gText_LucyWonSilver": "Humph",
    "gText_LucyDefeatSilver": "Urk",
    "gText_LucyWonGold": "Hah!",
    "gText_LucyDefeatGold": "Darn!",
    "gText_GretaWonSilver": "Oh, come on!\\nYou have to try harder than that!",
    "gText_GretaDefeatSilver": "No way!\\nGood job!",
    "gText_GretaWonGold": "Heheh!\\nWhat did you expect?",
    "gText_GretaDefeatGold": "Huh?\\nAre you serious?!",
    "gText_SpenserWonSilver": "Your POKMON are wimpy because\\nyou're wimpy as a TRAINER!",
    "gText_SpenserDefeatSilver": "Ah\\nNow this is something else",
    "gText_SpenserWonGold": "Gwahahaha!\\nMy brethren, we have nothing to fear!",
    "gText_SpenserDefeatGold": "Gwah!\\nHahahaha!",
    "gText_BrandonWonSilver": "Hey! What's wrong with you!\\nLet's see some effort! Get up!",
    "gText_BrandonDefeatSilver": "That's it! You've done great!\\nYou've worked hard for this!",
    "gText_BrandonWonGold": "Hey! Don't you give up now!\\nGet up! Don't lose faith in yourself!",
    "gText_BrandonDefeatGold": "That's it! You've done it!\\nYou kept working for this!",
